  "title": "Grants & Outreach Supervisor @ Kaki Bukit | 2 Years Contract",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Scope:</strong></h3><ul><li>Approve and overlook processing and verifying grant applications, maintaining accurate records, and communicating with applicants to gather required information.</li><li>Manage outreach programme  through on-site engagements and client engagements.</li><li>Coordinates with internal teams and external stakeholders to ensure smooth approval workflows and timely grant disbursement.</li><li>Handles enquiries, prepares reports for management, and supervise general administrative support to the grant team.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Minimum Diploma or equivalent</li><li>Detail-oriented with strong organizational and follow-up skills</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications (Excel, Word, Outlook)</li><li>Good written and verbal communication skills</li><li>Able to work independently and manage multiple tasks in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><h3><strong>Employment Details</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Work Days:</strong> Monday to Friday</li><li><strong>Work Hours:</strong> 8.30am – 6.00pm (Monday - Thursday), 8.30am – 5.30pm (Friday)</li><li><strong>Contract Duration:</strong> 2–year contract (Renewable)</li><li><strong>Work Location:</strong> Kaki Bukit/ Ubi</li><li>Salary Range: $3000 - $3,500</li></ul>",
